### Admin stats
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Admin teachers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/teachers
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Admin students
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/students
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Create admin student WITHOUT group (groupPublicId optional)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/students
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin_student_no_group",
  "email": "admin.student.nogroup@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Create admin student WITH group
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/students
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin_student_with_group",
  "email": "admin.student.withgroup@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "groupPublicId": "{{group_public_id}}"
}

### Create admin student - validation fail (bad email)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/students
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "",
  "email": "invalid",
  "password": ""
}

### Update admin student assignment (with group)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/students/15
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin_student_updated",
  "email": "admin.student.updated@example.com",
  "groupPublicId": "{{group_public_id}}"
}

### Update admin student - unassign from group (null groupPublicId)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/students/15
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin_student_updated",
  "email": "admin.student.updated@example.com",
  "groupPublicId": null
}

### Update admin student - forbidden (TEACHER token)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/students/15
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "hacker_attempt",
  "email": "hacker@example.com"
}
